def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.log(np.std(bins) + 1) + np.exp(item - np.mean(bins)) * item
```

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.cos(np.pi * (item / bins)) * np.sqrt(item) + np.mean(bins)
```

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.sin(np.pi * item) * np.exp(np.mean(bins) - item) + np.std(bins)
```

```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.log(item + 1) + np.cos(np.pi * (item / bins)) * np.mean(bins)
```

