### How to Measure Loss:
The loss is calculated as the total wasted space after packing all items. Lower loss is better.

### How to Choose the Best Heuristics:
The best heuristics are those that achieve the lowest loss. However, since we are to generate 10 unique functions, the selection is based on the uniqueness of the function implementation, not the actual loss.

