    return (item / np.mean(bins)) * np.exp(np.std(bins)) + np.log(item + np.max(bins)) * np.sin(np.pi * item)

This function uses a combination of division, multiplication, exponentiation, logarithm, and sine function, which is unique compared to other functions.

