5. Item to Bin Ratio:
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    # Compute the ratio of item to bin capacity
    ratio = item / bins
    # Higher priority to bins where the item fits well
    priority = np.minimum(ratio, 1)
    return priority

6. Proportional Fit:
